name: Starrelic - Stargrail
desc:
If a monster(s) is Special Summoned from the Extra Deck: You can Tribute this card; send that monster(s) to the GY. You can only use each of the following effects of "Starrelic - Stargrail" once per turn.
● If this face-up card that was Normal Summoned/Set leaves the field: You can Special Summon 2 "Stargrail" monsters from your Deck, except "Starrelic - Stargrail".
● During your Main Phase, except the turn this card was sent to the GY: You can banish this card from your GY; add 1 "Starrelic" card from your Deck to your hand.
